INSERT INTO public.blog (title,img,description,"date","content") VALUES 
('Best eSports Clans in the World: Top Teams','https://cdn.weareneon.com/app/uploads/2017/06/26094035/iem-katowice-counter-strike-global-offensive-teams-1350x536-min-1024x407.png','Best eSports clans in the world came to rise not only in a few years. They built the eSport arena to a new world. Since the start of eSport games, most of the people get involved with it. With time passed, most of them tried to teaming up together. Generally, with the development of multiplay, clan-based playing, and global network, the Clans started to come up. Thus, in there, the many eSport teams arrived to top. Let''s see who is at the top','2020-02-11','{"blocks":[{"key":"falvn","text":"Best eSports clans in the world came to rise not only in a few years. They built the eSport arena to a new world. Since the start of eSport games, most of the people get involved with it. With time passed, most of them tried to teaming up together. Generally, with the development of multiplay, clan-based playing, and global network, the Clans started to come up. Thus, in there, the many eSport teams arrived to top. Let''s see who is at the top","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2j8um","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"durbr","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9qvp6","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":1,"key":0}],"data":{}},{"key":"cgp0d","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cdajd","text":"Team Liquid","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"27mse","text":"Team Liquid is an eSports team from the Netherlands and founded in 2000. Back in 2001, they formed a community site, mainly focusing on StarCraft. After that, they created a Dota 2 team later, which was a remarkable turnaround. They hired a Dota team from North America. Thus they won a title in 2012. However, they had most tournaments participated and not much of the success. It was commonly known as the \"Fourth place curse\" by then.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"tm8v","text":"There were many changes in the Team Liquid. Many superstars involved with the team. In 2017 they won the biggest prize pool with the European Dota team. The more success bought them to the top. Overall when talking about clans, they became the best eSports clan in the world.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9n9jv","text":"Faze Clan","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"gl8r","text":"This clan is a US organization. It competes almost all the games in the world. Many games like Call of Duty, PUBG, Counter-Strike, Overwatch, Global Offensive. Well, I guess this clan has the most social marketing in eSports with comparing to other top teams. Many subscribers in twitch and youtube made them be at the top by involving with the gaming community. The beginning of the clan is also from YouTube. However, they are also one of the top teams in eSports around the world.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"97djc","text":"Fnatic","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"86rrs","text":"Fnatic is an eSports organization from London. It started its journey in 2004. They are the dominant team in Counter-Strike, League of Legends, Dota 2. Further, they won the inaugural League of Champions World Championship in 2011.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ephlf","text":"OG","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"f4ta9","text":"This OG te